productDes:
MANSORY presents a complete conversion on the basis of the Audi RSQ8 
•    Deep black paint with red decorative stripes 

• Interior design in leather/Alcantara in black/red 

 • Power increase to 780 PS and 1,000 Nm 

 •Performance: 0-100 km/h in 3.3 s and Vmax: 320 km/h

Engine - V12

Power - 425 kW / 570 hp

Mileage - 973 km

Registration date - 09/2021

0-100 km/h - 4,8s

Vmax

250 km/h / 155 mph

The MANSORY performance programme

 In keeping with the enhanced visual appearance, 

 MANSORY have also turned the screw in terms of performance. Instead of 544 PS (400 kW), 

 MANSORY 6x6 achieves an impressive 840 PS (618 kW), while the maximum torque 

 rises to an electronically limited 1,000 Newton metres.

The MANSORY performance programme

 Engine performance has also deserved the care of our specialists,

 who combined bigger turbochargers and a high performance sports exhaust 

 system with optimized electronics. The result is a really sonorous sound, a powerful 1,200 Nm

 of torque and a maximum speed of 280 km/h.

MANSORY Range Rover – Refinement programme

 Bonnet with ventilation inlets made entirely of carbon fibre

 Newly designed carbon applications on the entire vehicle

 Light alloy rims in "Type FD.15" design in 24" inch size

Power increase to 620 PS / 850 Nm

Performance: 0-100 km/h in 4.3s
